Package: aipet-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, python3-pip, nmap, systemd, ca-certificates
Maintainer: AIPET X <admin@aipet.io>
Homepage: https://aipet.io
Description: AIPET X security agent for IoT network scanning
 Lightweight agent that scans your local network for IoT devices,
 detects vulnerabilities, and reports findings to the AIPET X cloud.
 .
 Designed for healthcare, manufacturing, educational, and small
 enterprise organisations. Runs as a hardened systemd service under
 a dedicated unprivileged user (aipet-agent). Configuration lives in
 /etc/aipet-agent/agent.conf and is loaded as an EnvironmentFile.
 .
 After install, configure with: sudo aipet-agent setup
